  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium high heat.",
    "Add the beef strips and cook until browned, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced onion and cook until translucent, about 2 minutes.",
    "Add the diced tomato and cook until softened, about 2 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced aji amarillo pepper and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the marsala wine and pasta water emulsion and stir to combine.",
    "Add the soy sauce and stir to combine.",
    "Cook for an additional 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Serve the lomo saltado hot over rice or noodles."
